---
title: Harissa Chicken & Roasted Pumpkin with Spinach Couscous, Herby Mayo & Hazelnuts
description: Couscous is a lovely way to finish the day, but what if there was a bit of green? Add some spinach to pop against the vibrant orange of the roast pumpkin. Finally, crumble little clouds of feta on top for the perfect way to tie this dinner together.

*Unfortunately, this
week's almonds were in
short supply, so we've
replaced them with
hazelnuts. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
